{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840847501,"sessionID":"ses_287a34bbfffeJOt2Z1mqDFG4pL","part":{"id":"prt_d785ce656001JxE67xhNZ02hq0","messageID":"msg_d785cd97e001SwAKKcOWmsjKF0","sessionID":"ses_287a34bbfffeJOt2Z1mqDFG4pL","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-6fdda44120654922a0800660684a442b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-002/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-002/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # CodeInterpreter CRD Type Definition Design\n2: \n3: ## AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n4: \n5: **Module**: `pkg/apis`  \n6: **Language**: Go  \n7: **Size**: S  \n8: **Purpose**: Define Kubernetes CRD type definitions for CodeInterpreter resources, enable client-go code generation, and provide type-safe API access for code execution environment management.\n9: \n10: ## Architecture\n11: \n12: ### Package Structure\n13: \n14: ```\n15: pkg/apis/\n16: └── runtime/\n17:     └── v1alpha1/\n18:         ├── types.go                   # Core type definitions (AgentRuntime + Sandbox types)\n19:         ├── register.go                # Scheme registration\n20:         ├── doc.go                     # Package documentation\n21:         ├── deepcopy.go                # DeepCopy methods (generated)\n22:         └── types_test.go              # Unit tests\n23: ```\n24: \n25: ### API Group\n26: \n27: - **Group**: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n28: - **Version**: `v1alpha1`\n29: - **Scope**: `Namespaced`\n30: - **Kind**: `CodeInterpreter`\n31: - **Resource Plural**: `codeinterpreters`\n32: - **Short Names**: `ci`\n33: \n34: ### Component Interactions\n35: \n36: ```\n37: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n38: │                     Kubernetes API Server                   │\n39: │                                                             │\n40: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n41: │  │       runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1          │  │\n42: │  │  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │  │\n43: │  │  │  codeinterpreters.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh │  │  │\n44: │  │  └────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │  │\n45: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n46: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n47:                            │\n48:                            │ k8s client-go\n49:                            ▼\n50: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n51: │                  client-go (Generated)                     │\n52: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n53: │  │  clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/         │  │\n54: │  │    • CodeInterpreterInterface                        │  │\n55: │  │    • REST CRUD + Watch                               │  │\n56: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n57: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n58: │  │  informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/        │  │\n59: │  │    • CodeInterpreterInformer                         │  │\n60: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n61: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n62: │  │  listers/runtime/v1alpha1/                          │  │\n63: │  │    • CodeInterpreterLister                           │  │\n64: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n65: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n66:                            │\n67:                            │ Controllers\n68:                            ▼\n69: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n70: │                   Code Execution Components                 │\n71: │  ┌─────────────────┐  ┌─────────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐ │\n72: │  │  PicoD Daemon   │  │  Session Store  │  │  Router     │ │\n73: │  │  (per pod)      │  │  (Redis)        │  │  (Nginx)    │ │\n74: │  └─────────────────┘  └─────────────────┘  └─────────────┘ │\n75: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n76: ```\n77: \n78: ## Data Structures\n79: \n80: ### CodeInterpreter\n81: \n82: **File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n83: \n84: ```go\n85: // +genclient\n86: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n87: // +k8s:openapi-gen=true\n88: // +kubebuilder:resource:shortName=ci;codeinterpreter\n89: // +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n90: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Ready\",type=\"boolean\",JSONPath=\".status.ready\"\n91: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Runtime\",type=\"string\",JSONPath=\".spec.runtime\"\n92: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n93: \n94: // CodeInterpreter defines a custom resource for managing code execution environments.\n95: // It represents a code interpreter sandbox that executes user code in a secure environment.\n96: type CodeInterpreter struct {\n97:     metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n98:     metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n99: \n100:     Spec   CodeInterpreterSpec   `json:\"spec,omitempty\"`\n101:     Status CodeInterpreterStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n102: }\n103: \n104: // CodeInterpreterSpec defines the desired state of a CodeInterpreter.\n105: type CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n106:     // Image is the container image for the interpreter (e.g., \"python:3.11-slim\").\n107:     // +required\n108:     Image string `json:\"image\"`\n109: \n110:     // Runtime specifies the execution environment type.\n111:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"python\"\n112:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=python;javascript;typescript;go\n113:     // +optional\n114:     Runtime string `json:\"runtime,omitempty\"`\n115: \n116:     // Timeout defines the maximum execution time for code snippets.\n117:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"5m\"\n118:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Type=string\n119:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Format=duration\n120:     // +optional\n121:     Timeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"timeout,omitempty\"`\n122: \n123:     // Resources defines compute resource requirements for the interpreter container.\n124:     // +optional\n125:     Resources *SandboxContainerResources `json:\"resources,omitempty\"`\n126: \n127:     // Env defines environment variables to inject into the interpreter container.\n128:     // +optional\n129:     Env []SandboxEnvVar `json:\"env,omitempty\"`\n130: \n131:     // EnabledPackages specifies allowed packages for the interpreter.\n132:     // Only packages listed here can be imported/required. Empty list allows all.\n133:     // +optional\n134:     EnabledPackages []string `json:\"enabledPackages,omitempty\"`\n135: }\n136: \n137: // CodeInterpreterStatus defines the observed state of a CodeInterpreter.\n138: type CodeInterpreterStatus struct {\n139:     // Ready indicates whether the interpreter is ready to execute code.\n140:     // +optional\n141:     Ready bool `json:\"ready,omitempty\"`\n142: \n143:     // Conditions represent the latest available observations of the CodeInterpreter's current state.\n144:     // +optional\n145:     Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n146: \n147:     // ObservedGeneration is the most recent generation observed by the controller.\n148:     // +optional\n149:     ObservedGeneration int64 `json:\"observedGeneration,omitempty\"`\n150: }\n151: \n152: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n153: \n154: // CodeInterpreterList contains a list of CodeInterpreter objects.\n155: type CodeInterpreterList struct {\n156:     metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n157:     metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n158: \n159:     Items []CodeInterpreter `json:\"items\"`\n160: }\n161: ```\n162: \n163: ### SandboxContainerResources (Reused from AgentRuntime)\n164: \n165: ```go\n166: // SandboxContainerResources defines resource requirements for a container.\n167: type SandboxContainerResources struct {\n168:     // Limits defines the resource limits.\n169:     // +optional\n170:     Limits SandboxResourceList `json:\"limits,omitempty\"`\n171: \n172:     // Requests defines the resource requests.\n173:     // +optional\n174:     Requests SandboxResourceList `json:\"requests,omitempty\"`\n175: }\n176: \n177: // SandboxResourceList defines a list of resources.\n178: type SandboxResourceList struct {\n179:     // CPU defines CPU resources.\n180:     // +optional\n181:     CPU string `json:\"cpu,omitempty\"`\n182: \n183:     // Memory defines memory resources.\n184:     // +optional\n185:     Memory string `json:\"memory,omitempty\"`\n186: \n187:     // EphemeralStorage defines ephemeral storage resources.\n188:     // +optional\n189:     EphemeralStorage string `json:\"ephemeralStorage,omitempty\"`\n190: }\n191: ```\n192: \n193: ### SandboxEnvVar (Reused from AgentRuntime)\n194: \n195: ```go\n196: // SandboxEnvVar defines an environment variable.\n197: type SandboxEnvVar struct {\n198:     // Name is the name of the environment variable.\n199:     // +required\n200:     Name string `json:\"name\"`\n201: \n202:     // Value is the literal value of the environment variable.\n203:     // +optional\n204:     Value string `json:\"value,omitempty\"`\n205: \n206:     // ValueFrom specifies a source for the value.\n207:     // +optional\n208:     ValueFrom *SandboxEnvVarSource `json:\"valueFrom,omitempty\"`\n209: }\n210: \n211: // SandboxEnvVarSource defines a source for environment variable values.\n212: type SandboxEnvVarSource struct {\n213:     // FieldRef selects a field from the pod.\n214:     // +optional\n215:     FieldRef *SandboxFieldRef `json:\"fieldRef,omitempty\"`\n216: \n217:     // ConfigMapKeyRef selects a key from a ConfigMap.\n218:     // +optional\n219:     ConfigMapKeyRef *SandboxConfigMapKeyRef `json:\"configMapKeyRef,omitempty\"`\n220: \n221:     // SecretKeyRef selects a key from a Secret.\n222:     // +optional\n223:     SecretKeyRef *SandboxSecretKeyRef `json:\"secretKeyRef,omitempty\"`\n224: }\n225: ```\n226: \n227: ### Scheme Registration\n228: \n229: **File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go`\n230: \n231: ```go\n232: package v1alpha1\n233: \n234: import (\n235:     metav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n236:     k8sruntime \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime\"\n237:     \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema\"\n238:     \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/serializer\"\n239:     k8sutil \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/util/runtime\"\n240: )\n241: \n242: var (\n243:     SchemeBuilder = k8sruntime.NewSchemeBuilder(addKnownTypes)\n244:     AddToScheme   = SchemeBuilder.AddToScheme\n245: )\n246: \n247: // SchemeGroupVersion is group version used to register these objects.\n248: var SchemeGroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}\n249: \n250: // Resource takes an unqualified resource and returns a Group qualified GroupResource.\n251: func Resource(resource string) schema.GroupResource {\n252:     return SchemeGroupVersion.WithResource(resource).GroupResource()\n253: }\n254: \n255: var (\n256:     // Scheme is the runtime.Scheme for the API types.\n257:     Scheme = k8sruntime.NewScheme()\n258: \n259:     // Codecs provides methods for retrieving codecs and serializers for the scheme.\n260:     Codecs = serializer.NewCodecFactory(Scheme)\n261: \n262:     // ParameterCodec handles versioning of objects that are converted to query parameters.\n263:     ParameterCodec = k8sruntime.NewParameterCodec(Scheme)\n264: )\n265: \n266: func init() {\n267:     // Add the Kubernetes types to the scheme.\n268:     metav1.AddToGroupVersion(Scheme, schema.GroupVersion{Version: \"v1\"})\n269:     k8sutil.Must(AddToScheme(Scheme))\n270: }\n271: \n272: // addKnownTypes adds the set of known types to the supplied scheme.\n273: func addKnownTypes(scheme *k8sruntime.Scheme) error {\n274:     scheme.AddKnownTypes(SchemeGroupVersion,\n275:         &AgentRuntime{},\n276:         &AgentRuntimeList{},\n277:         &CodeInterpreter{},\n278:         &CodeInterpreterList{},\n279:     )\n280:     metav1.AddToGroupVersion(scheme, SchemeGroupVersion)\n281:     return nil\n282: }\n283: ```\n284: \n285: **File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go`\n286: \n287: ```go\n288: // Package v1alpha1 contains API Schema definitions for the runtime v1alpha1 API group.\n289: //\n290: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen=package\n291: // +k8s:conversion-gen=github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis\n292: // +k8s:openapi-gen=true\n293: // +k8s:defaulter-gen=TypeMeta\n294: // +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n295: package v1alpha1\n296: ```\n297: \n298: ## API Contracts\n299: \n300: ### CRD Manifest\n301: \n302: **CodeInterpreter CRD** (generated by `controller-gen`)\n303: \n304: ```yaml\n305: apiVersion: apiextensions.k8s.io/v1\n306: kind: CustomResourceDefinition\n307: metadata:\n308:   annotations:\n309:     controller-gen.kubebuilder.io/version: v0.17.2\n310:   name: codeinterpreters.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n311: spec:\n312:   group: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n313:   names:\n314:     kind: CodeInterpreter\n315:     listKind: CodeInterpreterList\n316:     plural: codeinterpreters\n317:     shortNames:\n318:     - ci\n319:     singular: codeinterpreter\n320:   scope: Namespaced\n321:   versions:\n322:   - name: v1alpha1\n323:     schema:\n324:       openAPIV3Schema:\n325:         description: CodeInterpreter defines a custom resource for managing code execution environments.\n326:         properties:\n327:           apiVersion:\n328:             description: 'APIVersion defines the versioned schema of this representation\n329:               of an object.'\n330:             type: string\n331:           kind:\n332:         