{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840872589,"sessionID":"ses_287a34bbfffeJOt2Z1mqDFG4pL","part":{"id":"prt_d785d2933001iGr5Vts1VZh3jV","messageID":"msg_d785d1bdf0012n28HxmHK5vxWu","sessionID":"ses_287a34bbfffeJOt2Z1mqDFG4pL","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-30c3508eb02d4a07aad8e2cef6ce7b61","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量\n\n## Metadata\n- **AR**: AR-003\n- **Title**: CRD 共享类型与常量\n- **Module**: pkg/apis\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: S\n- **Status**: Pending\n\n## Description\nDefine shared types and constants for CRD resources in the AgentCube project.\n\n## Dependencies\nNone\n\n## Related Changes\nNone","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-003/CHANGE.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-003/CHANGE.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-003/CHANGE.md","time":{"start":1775840872563,"end":1775840872588}}}}
